# .tmux-layout - Per-project tmux window config
# Place in project root. Sessionizer reads this when creating a session.
# Format: window_name: command
# Lines without a command just open a shell.

# Example: frontend project
# code:
# claude: claude
# dev: npm run dev
# storybook: npm run storybook
# term:

# Example: CDK project
# code:
# claude: claude
# synth: cdk watch
# term:
